Package de.gym.backend

Class User

java.lang.Object
de.gym.backend.User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Employee
public class User
extends java.lang.Object
The User class represents the attributes a normal user has, when he logges in the gymApp. By normal user, it is meant the person who attends the gym, the client. A user can have different roles besides client, such as employee of the gym or trainer.
Author:
florina
